'''美国采暖、制冷与空调工程师学会'''（American Society of Heating, Refrigerating and Air-Conditioning Engineers）簡稱'''ASHRAE'''，於1894年在美國紐約成立<ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9A03E1DB123DE433A25750C2A9679C94649ED7CF|title=PURE AIR FOR TENEMENTS; THE SUGGESTIONS OF E.P. BATES TO FELLOW ENGINEERS.|date=1895-01-23|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2009-08-15|archive-date=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108042749/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9A03E1DB123DE433A25750C2A9679C94649ED7CF|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是由[[暖通空調|暖通空調]]（HVAC）工程師所組成的學會，全球的會員超過五萬人，學會主要注重在樓宇系統、能源效率、[[室內空氣品質|室內空氣品質]]、[[冷凍|冷凍]]及[[可持續性|可持續性]]。

